{"tid":1415952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說 光復香港時代革命 試著說 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:26:38.000Z","uid":278201,"like":48,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"16605577e5de774bebc00c00be9c3c45f5916c02","tid":1415952,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"利申返p牌仔先 要屌分化就屌啦<br />\n首先唔反對玩火系魔法同石系物理攻擊 明白前線要buy time撒退<br />\n但係時代革命句口號太易每日記者會洗腦話港獨 然後中立或者淺黃會動搖<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩唔洗理民意 到依家仲掌握住風向優勢 正正就係因為有民意<br />\n<br />\n所以 倒不如叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n一來出師有名<br />\n二來可以提返自己爭取緊啲咩<br />\n<br />\n狗只係港共前面嘅最後一個boss 但係我地目標係打大佬 撚狗之餘 唔好唔記得港共先會重點<br />\n<br />\n有咩錯漏 歡迎屌醒討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bccfde8cd0144837a07fc2237fd744eab04a67","tid":1415952,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"人手十連"},{"pid":"9bb56c50d99457898cdbf29dd98e7adb76190a07","tid":1415952,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"393e69f881363002c31ae7b40e9748fdd0d12fd2","tid":1415952,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"452596393b210e6e93574a8c382298c53109d5b8","tid":1415952,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c9e9482edef045f7930d7c7a256c6812458e60e9","tid":1415952,"uid":51731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"真係唔好講革命啦"},{"pid":"d47ab72a4d44d8a7907325bd54ca0482b4337367","tid":1415952,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:29.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f77b8455ff63b3e0460015d95ce7d98bfb5b87c9","tid":1415952,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14